node.text:
A simple, but awesome spirit-forward sipper, right by the ocean in Venice Beach. Some things just feel right.
@koko.marshall is making this at the super chill @granblancovenice

JOHNNY BUTE
• Rittenhouse Rye
• Aromatic Bitters
• Palo Santo Mist

Video and Music: @BarMaxExtra
.

node.text:
Few things are more refreshing than a perfectly executed Tiki classic. Cocktail Director Matthew made this Jungle Bird for me at the brand new and very beautiful @thegrant_la

JUNGLE BIRD
• Dark Rum
• Campari
• Pineapple
• Lime
• Simple Syrup

Video and Music: @BarMaxExtra
.

node.text:
This frisky Rooster knows how to party.

CHICK MAGNET
• 2 oz Rooster Rojo Añejo Tequila with smoked Pineapple @rooster.rojo
• 1 oz Grapefruit Liqueur
• 1 oz Ginger Liqueur
• 1 oz Lemon Juice
• Few drops of Saline
• Torched Absinthe Rinse
Garnish: Fresh Pineapple Wheel and Tajin

Video and Music: @BarMaxExtra @BarMaxLA

.

Check out this unusual Margarita that Bar Director Sebastian Ramirez @ramradixx shook up for me at the Bar at Citrin in West LA. @citrinla is a fantastic new concept by Chef Josiah Citrin, creator of famed two-Michelin-star culinary landmark Melisse.
Citrin has a great Happy Hour, every day, starting at 5.

MIDNIGHT MARGARITA
• Tequila
• Cointreau
• Agave
• Lime
• Activated Charcoal
• Citrus Foam

Video and Music: @BarMaxExtra
.

LA SOUR
• Gin
• All Natural Blue Spirulina Powder
• Lemon
• Egg White
• SimpleSyrup
• Aromatic Bitters

Video and Music: @BarMaxExtra
.

node.text:
This frisky Rooster knows how to party.

CHICK MAGNET
• 2 oz Rooster Rojo Añejo Tequila with smoked Pineapple @rooster.rojo
• 1 oz Grapefruit Liqueur
• 1 oz Ginger Liqueur
• 1 oz Lemon Juice
• Few drops of Saline
• Torched Absinthe Rinse
Garnish: Fresh Pineapple Wheel and Tajin

Video and Music: @BarMaxExtra @BarMaxLA

.
